headline: Tech Stock Rally Is Just Beginning, Wedbush's Ives Says
summary: Dan Ives, Wedbush Securities managing director and global head of tech research, expects tech stocks to perform strongly in the second half of the year. Speaking on "Bloomberg The Close," Ives says AI is creating a "Game of Thrones arms race." He also discusses the outlook for Uber and IBM.
